text: At least 3 people who were behind me got their orders first. Waited 30mins for a plate of super salty fish mee hoon noodle. Never will i visit this rubbish place again!

Decent food at decent prices. Nothing to shout about. The coffeeshop is located right beside a dumpster so pray that the dump truck does not come when you are having your meal. I was there on a Friday evening at about 6.30pm and the dump truck spent a good 10 minutes there and the smell was just slightly revolting
$10 Hor fun come with  4small frozen praws, few slice of fish cake,  pork card chye SIM. Not value for money. Won't be back again.
Very reasonable and tasty Zi Cha food . Their dark hokkien Mee is their speciality.
